src/parallel/zsc-dgr-src/differentials.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Obtain the differential terms necessary for the interfacial force calculation (the Laplacian and the gradient of the order parameter phi_f) in the dual grid parallel D2Q5/D2Q9 Zheng-Shu-Chew multiphase LBM.The calculation is done directly on the order parameter grid.
